aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050b80b30e2ee32cfbcc51ed8520995ad2b9092e","tid":154704,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T00:21:22.000Z","msg":"20年後會有一間珠寶店叫康生生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdb01462b366a43bfdaefe7ceb8a33573ce829b","tid":154704,"uid":28555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細路黎講佢都算樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得幾精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ef6383e8d0d88e0357a0cd421f903028705e6f","tid":154704,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T00:25:46.000Z","msg":"我成日都覺得佢同關平好似樣&hellip;"},{"pid":"6be53528f65b2718da002d955c7aa5c5cb153c2a","tid":154704,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日都覺得佢同關平好似樣&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3639b76f8f2d87e1f47291f5d2cc350f72bc9b","tid":154704,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"1966年，「無產階級文化大革命」爆發。這一年的5月28日，中央文革小組成立，康生出任小組顧問，他對文革小組的決策給予了很大的支持。<br />\n<br />\n在8月舉行的中共八屆十一中全會上，康生躋身中共中央政治局常委之列。<br />\n<br />\n1968年獲得了中共首要情報機關中共中央調查部的領導權，製造了大量的冤案，成為在黨內鬥爭中令人畏懼的「劊子手」。<br />\n<br />\n1967年初，先把賀龍打為國民黨、軍閥。後期並製造了六十一人叛徒集團案，導致大批老幹部被關進監獄。後以此指責劉少奇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81256053495dcbd197acf7b845ffbff0a2b93c1b","tid":154704,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1966年，「無產階級文化大革命」爆發。這一年的5月28日，中央文革小組成立，康生出任小組顧問，他對文革小組的決策給予了很大的支持。<br />\n<br />\n在8月舉行的中共八屆十一中全會上，康生躋身中共中央政治局常委之列。<br />\n<br />\n1968年獲得了中共首要情報機關中共中央調查部的領導權，製造了大量的冤案，成為在黨內鬥爭中令人畏懼的「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">劊子手</span></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n1967年初，先把賀龍打為國民黨、軍閥。後期並製造了六十一人叛徒集團案，導致大批老幹部被關進監獄。後以此指責劉少奇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d4eaba27c57e5de07d1d499284c17889ce2eb51","tid":154704,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/25/134728_5bb5ce802313107bfb63f95bbd00575a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F25%2F134728_5bb5ce802313107bfb63f95bbd00575a.jpg&h=1cb022ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2e324VD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2e324VD.jpg&h=d2ec9d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a23566766345c93fade673b82b3e1dad9dff5a5","tid":154704,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"套膠劇幾時完呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1412c79cc33ac2a397112c2fc9929e81138c853","tid":154704,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"識人叫杜康生 覺得幾好聽<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d1adb147f015a7fb48cc6f9bcb3134fb594856","tid":154704,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:15:48.000Z